Create a SAML attribute from the components.

Parameters:
name - The name of the attribute.
nameFormat - The name format of the attribute, may be null.
friendlyName - The human-readable form of the attribute's name, may be null.
otherXMLAttrs - Other XML attributes to be used with this SAMLAttribute. Maps xml-attribute-ids to xml-attribute-values. Can be null.
attributeValues - The list of SAMLAttributeValues, may be null.
